node.text:
Imagine a problem, a concern, or hurdle you currently have in your life.  That problem concern or hurdle is equal to your current level of awareness (consciousness) as it relates to that problem.  When we know how to expand our feeling inside our body, our inspiration, our joy, we can then become more expansive than the level of consciousness we were holding when we perceived the issue as a problem, concern, or hurdle in our lives. This doesn’t mean we don’t need to address the issue, but when we expand our level of awareness all of a sudden what we once perceived as a problem is now a simple pebble in the middle of the road we simply need to step over. 

Follow @DavidSamuelStraus  for more daily wisdom!

What is your takeaway from this video? Share it with me in the comments below!👇

node.title: How to solve a problem with @DavidSamuelStraus 🧐

node.text:
Your language to the universe is frequency! The word consciousness is thrown about so casually that it’s easy to lose sight of what it means, even more so when it is defined as being “awakened.” Awakened consciousness is a state of being aware that you are aware. It is a realization that you are the watcher, the witness within you—not the analyzer, not the thinker, not even the meditator, but that which is the impartial witness of every aspect of your being and doing. 

Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more!

node.title: Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more wisdom on the law of attraction!✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I am quirky, blunt, and broken. My days are sometimes too dark, and my nights are sometimes too long. I often trip over my own insecurities. require attention, long for passion, and wish to be desired.. love hard and with all that have and even with my faults, am worth loving. DANU GIBSON THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Never give up on a dream because of the time it will take to accomplish it. The time will pass anyway. EARL LNIGHTINGALE NIGHT THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'We've all been hurt, we've all been disappointed and I am sure we all at some point of our lives said, "I don't ever want to feel this way again." We set an intention for ourselves of how 'we don't want to feel' instead of how we want to feel'. Intentions guide our thoughts, attitudes, choices and create our outcomes. written by Nansia Movidi'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'That's what people do who love you. They put their arms around you and love you when you're not so lovable. Deb Caletti, The Fortunes of Indigo Skye'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'There's a difference between interest and commitment. Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'May your choices reflect your hopes, not your fears. NELSON MANDELA THEGOODQUOTE'.
